data.description: The Texas limestone exterior on this large corner lot welcomes you to the spacious interior. The interior greets you with an inviting and open floor plan. The main living area boasts high ceilings, abundant natural light, and a cozy stone fireplace. Combined with the extra living/family room there is ample space for entertaining friends and family. The large kitchen and pantry provide an abundance of storage, style, and functionality. The versatility of the kitchen and pantry are sure to impress. The Master bedroom, with its double door entry, offers a peaceful and secluded sanctuary after a long day. The ensuite bathroom is complete with a spa-like soaking tub, separate shower, and dual vanities. The spacious walk in closet off the master bathroom caps off the master suite. The front bedroom, complete with French doors, provides the versatility for a home office or game room. The backyard retreat with covered patio and extended decking is perfect for entertaining, while the privacy fence provides seclusion for relaxing evenings. Furthermore, the side facing garage ensures the desirability of this meticulously maintained home. The Windmill Farms subdivision with community pool/park, within minutes to Lake Belton, and Belton ISD schools make this one of the most highly desirable locations in all of Central Texas!
